            <abstract id="ref53" label="Abstract">Scot Borofsky is a grafitti, studio, and commercial artist. This small collection documents his career in New York City and other places his artwork has been shown.</abstract>
        </did>
        <arrangement id="ref43">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>This collection is arranged into three series:</p>
            <list type="ordered">
                <item>Series I: Catalogs</item>
                <item>Series II: Portfolio</item>
                <item>Series III: Media</item>
            </list>
            <p>Series I is arranged chronologically. Series II is in the original order in which it was organized in Scot Borofsky's portfolio.</p>
        </arrangement>
